1
00:00:00,410 --> 00:00:03,510
Chae Hwa Young, have you ever heard
of the "fruit of the poisonous tree?"

2
00:00:03,840 --> 00:00:07,650
Yes, any confession or recording
we force out of you...

3
00:00:07,850 --> 00:00:09,710
might be considered the "poisonous fruit."

4
00:00:10,180 --> 00:00:12,120
But when Jang Mi uses it...

5
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:13,820
to find independent physical evidence,

6
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:16,520
it becomes a whole different story.

7
00:00:16,720 --> 00:00:21,290
For example, the weapon
you used to murder Bok Gil,

8
00:00:21,590 --> 00:00:23,530
the testimony and medical records...

9
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:25,360
from the doctor
you bribed to help kill Seo Rin,

10
00:00:25,530 --> 00:00:26,970
or secondarily derived evidence...

11
00:00:26,970 --> 00:00:30,200
like the hidden bank accounts
of the people you hired.

12
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:32,540
All of that
would be perfectly admissible in court.

13
00:00:33,170 --> 00:00:35,470
- But that...
- Grandfather probably has made...

14
00:00:35,470 --> 00:00:37,510
Manager Lee a very tempting offer
about now.

15
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:40,380
That if he's the first one
to confess everything,

16
00:00:40,550 --> 00:00:42,310
he can avoid jail time
and start over abroad.

17
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:44,650
And that my grandfather would give him
a huge amount of money...

18
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:46,150
so he could live in luxury.

19
00:00:46,790 --> 00:00:48,320
From Manager Lee's perspective,

20
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:51,690
wouldn't betraying you
be the much better deal?

21
00:00:51,690 --> 00:00:53,060
No, that's not true.

22
00:00:53,730 --> 00:00:56,730
Manager Lee would never betray me.
He's mine.

23
00:00:57,060 --> 00:01:00,100
There's absolutely no way.
Stop trying to drive a wedge between us.

24
00:01:00,170 --> 00:01:01,970
You have such absolute faith
in Lee Kang Hyuk.

25
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:05,540
I'm curious, too.
We'll see if he lives up to that.

26
00:01:06,700 --> 00:01:11,240
Crooks like you two act like
the best of friends,

27
00:01:11,410 --> 00:01:12,980
but you'll betray each other
in a heartbeat.

28
00:01:13,910 --> 00:01:18,420
Especially a born thug like Lee Kang Hyuk.

29
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,750
Stop talking nonsense.

30
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:24,360
- Do you really think I'll fall for that?
- Alright then, shall we find out?

31
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,660
Whether Lee Kang Hyuk
has turned on you or not.

32
00:01:27,130 --> 00:01:31,730
Let's see just how long he can hold out
against my grandfather.

33
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:40,340
Lee Kang Hyuk, I'll ask you again.

34
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:43,880
Where is the weapon used
to murder Jang Mi's father?

35
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:45,610
I don't know.

36
00:01:46,410 --> 00:01:47,680
I don't know anything about that.

37
00:01:47,850 --> 00:01:50,650
You murdered Oh Bok Gil
with Chae Hwa Young.

38
00:01:51,380 --> 00:01:53,050
You were with her at the site.

39
00:01:53,050 --> 00:01:55,550
- Why are you playing dumb?
- That never happened.

40
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,160
And...

41
00:01:59,090 --> 00:02:01,090
Hwa Young would never do
something like that.

42
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:03,290
"Chae Hwa Young would never do
something like that."

43
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,260
That's right.

44
00:02:09,170 --> 00:02:11,300
Because Chae Hwa Young
just confessed everything.

45
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:14,270
She said the person who killed Oh Bok Gil
with a wrench...

46
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:15,940
was you, Lee Kang Hyuk.

47
00:02:17,140 --> 00:02:18,140
What?

48
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,580
Hwa Young said that?

49
00:02:22,850 --> 00:02:24,850
That can't be right. Stop lying.

50
00:02:24,850 --> 00:02:26,750
I told you.

51
00:02:28,050 --> 00:02:32,060
Chae Hwa Young has lived a pampered life.

52
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:34,960
I knew she wouldn't last a few hours.

53
00:02:37,330 --> 00:02:39,300
So, Lawyer Kang?

54
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:42,600
Did she say who killed Seo Rin?

55
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:45,970
That it was this bastard, Lee Kang Hyuk?

56
00:02:47,110 --> 00:02:50,440
She hasn't gotten to that part yet,
but I think she will soon.

57
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:52,780
Right now, she's crawling on the floor...

58
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:54,650
begging for forgiveness.

59
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,080
Kang Baek Ho.

60
00:02:58,650 --> 00:03:01,190
What did you do to my Hwa Young?

61
00:03:01,250 --> 00:03:03,860
Hey, you pathetic fool.

62
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:07,390
You still have the energy to yell?

63
00:03:07,990 --> 00:03:09,090
How pathetic.

64
00:03:09,390 --> 00:03:10,400
Lee Kang Hyuk.

65
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,400
You need to think carefully.

66
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:17,140
Chae Hwa Young is pinning everything
on you right now.

67
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:18,900
Hwa Young,

68
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:23,780
you're not really going to pin this all
on me, are you?

69
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:27,780
So tell me the truth, Lee Kang Hyuk.

70
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,080
The wrench used to strike Oh Bok Gil.

71
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:31,820
Where did you hide it?

72
00:03:32,820 --> 00:03:33,820
I don't know.

73
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:35,950
I told you, I don't know.

74
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:40,590
You just heard that Chae Hwa Young
has started talking.

75
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:41,930
You bastard.

76
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:46,060
Are you going to play dumb
until the very end?

77
00:03:46,830 --> 00:03:48,300
That can't be true.

78
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:50,670
You're not going to...

79
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:54,370
make me talk this way.

80
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:55,770
Neither I nor CEO Chae...

81
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:59,780
- know anything about it.
- Is that so?

82
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:03,450
Secretary Kim, make the call.

83
00:04:13,490 --> 00:04:14,490
Yes, Grandfather.

84
00:04:14,790 --> 00:04:15,790
All right.

85
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:17,430
Are you ready?

86
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:20,130
Yes. Go ahead.

87
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:26,940
Listen, CEO Chae.

88
00:04:27,710 --> 00:04:29,940
You should have done this sooner.

89
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,810
If you confess even now,

90
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:35,610
I'll show you some leniency.

91
00:04:36,150 --> 00:04:37,350
Our Seo Rin...

92
00:04:38,050 --> 00:04:39,280
Who killed her?

93
00:04:39,780 --> 00:04:41,890
- Tell me.
- Father.

94
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:44,290
It wasn't me.

95
00:04:44,890 --> 00:04:47,190
Kang Hyuk took her behind my back...

96
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:49,630
and killed Seo Rin.

97
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,060
He said he did it for me.

98
00:04:52,930 --> 00:04:54,130
So...

99
00:04:54,530 --> 00:04:57,740
you're saying Lee Kang Hyuk
killed Seo Rin?

100
00:04:58,240 --> 00:05:00,370
When I was trying to trick you
into thinking I was your daughter,

101
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:02,740
Seo Rin found out about it,

102
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:05,540
so I asked Kang Hyuk what I should do.

103
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:10,280
But I never thought he'd take Seo Rin
and kill her.

104
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,050
I resented him and even hit him then.

105
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:16,050
I asked how he could kill my own daughter.

106
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,920
All right, in that case,

107
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:22,960
will you provide the evidence for that?

108
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:25,400
Yes, I will.

109
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,270
So please, let me go.

110
00:05:28,970 --> 00:05:33,600
I want to get out of here right now.
Father, please save me.

111
00:05:34,670 --> 00:05:37,180
All right, one more question.

112
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:41,880
When you were pretending to be Eun Hye...

113
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:43,920
and trying to take over Dream,

114
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:46,380
whose idea was that?

115
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,990
That was also Kang Hyuk's idea.

116
00:05:49,690 --> 00:05:53,420
The truth is, Kang Hyuk gaslit me.

117
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:57,760
I think Kang Hyuk wanted to use me
to get ahead.

118
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:01,400
He used me because
he couldn't do it on his own.

119
00:06:02,330 --> 00:06:05,040
I was deceived. It's not fair.

120
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:10,040
Lee Kang Hyuk planned everything
and gaslit me into executing it.

121
00:06:10,740 --> 00:06:13,880
I was just a fool
for listening to Lee Kang Hyuk...

122
00:06:17,010 --> 00:06:18,180
That's a lie.

123
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:20,950
No, that's a lie.

124
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:27,330
So, all of these crimes...

125
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:31,500
- were committed by Kang Hyuk, right?
- Yes, Chairman.

126
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:33,360
Please, give me one more chance.

127
00:06:33,770 --> 00:06:35,270
I don't know anything.

128
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:38,140
Kang Hyuk made me do it.

129
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:40,340
Manager Lee did everything.

130
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:43,910
I was just doing whatever
Manager Lee told me to do.

131
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:48,410
Yes, Chairman.
So, you're going to let me go now, right?

132
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,350
I'm begging you, Chairman.

133
00:06:53,650 --> 00:06:57,920
Jang Mi, you're incredible.
You sound just like Chae Hwa Young.

134
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:02,690
If I feed a sample of
Chae Hwa Young's voice into this app,

135
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:05,630
my voice comes out sounding
just like hers.

136
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:10,400
Of course, my delivery has to be perfect
to trick Manager Lee.

137
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:14,710
Anyway, do you think
Lee Kang Hyuk bought it?

138
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:17,240
Either way, he must be really shaken up.

139
00:07:17,740 --> 00:07:20,510
He heard Chae Hwa Young, the one person
who would never betray him,

140
00:07:21,150 --> 00:07:22,580
do exactly that.

141
00:07:24,150 --> 00:07:25,150
Baek Ho.

142
00:07:25,780 --> 00:07:27,320
How is Lee Kang Hyuk holding up
over there?

143
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:30,120
Did he react to hearing
Chae Hwa Young's voice?

144
00:07:30,790 --> 00:07:32,190
I think he's really rattled.

145
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:34,690
Looks like the prisoner's dilemma strategy
is working, right?

146
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:37,200
I'll tell Lee Kang Hyuk...

147
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:41,530
that Chae Hwa Young is trying
to pin everything on him...

148
00:07:41,570 --> 00:07:43,300
and then I'll ask how he killed Seo Rin.

149
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:45,740
So, Jang Mi, you go to Chae Hwa Young,

150
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:49,040
tell her the false information
Lee Kang Hyuk revealed the evidence...

151
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:50,410
and get the real evidence from her.

152
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:54,080
Yes. We're already halfway there.

153
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:57,250
Now let's tighten the reins
on Chae Hwa Young a little more.

154
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:58,580
Got it.

155
00:08:10,930 --> 00:08:12,330
(Minutes
of the General Shareholders' Meeting)

156
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:15,030
What's this?

157
00:08:15,030 --> 00:08:16,030
"Choi Ha Joon?"

158
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,500
(Minutes
of the General Shareholders' Meeting)

159
00:08:18,570 --> 00:08:19,840
(Shareholders: Choi Ha Joon, by proxy,
Ma Dae Chang, in person)

160
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:23,040
The person you are calling is unavailable.

161
00:08:23,110 --> 00:08:25,540
- Why is Manager Lee so hard to reach?
- Connecting to voicemail.

162
00:08:25,710 --> 00:08:26,710
Team Leader Jin.

163
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,310
What are you doing here?

164
00:08:28,810 --> 00:08:30,620
Hey, what is this?

165
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,720
- What are you doing?
- You knew that Baek Ho...

166
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:36,790
Yes, I know that Kang Baek Ho
is Choi Ha Joon,

167
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:37,860
the majority shareholder.

168
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,490
But why didn't you tell me?

169
00:08:40,890 --> 00:08:44,060
Because if you knew,
CEO Chae would find out.

170
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:45,760
And if CEO Chae knew,

171
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:47,900
I was afraid of what she might do
to Baek Ho again.

172
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:49,330
That's why I couldn't tell you.

173
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:51,040
You know...

174
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,770
that I love Baek Ho.

175
00:08:54,210 --> 00:08:57,580
What you love isn't Kang Baek Ho,
it's his money.

176
00:08:58,540 --> 00:09:01,780
Now that he's the majority shareholder
of Dream Group.

177
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,810
Is that what you really think of me?

178
00:09:04,580 --> 00:09:08,620
I've liked him since way back,
when he was just an ordinary lawyer.

179
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:10,490
Don't make me out to be so shallow.

180
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:15,490
Of course, the fact that he's
the majority shareholder of Dream Hotel...

181
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,700
did reignite the feelings
I had given up on, I admit.

182
00:09:21,130 --> 00:09:22,130
But...

183
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:25,370
when was the last time you saw
CEO Chae at home?

184
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,670
CEO Chae?

185
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:28,640
She went to New York.

186
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:31,640
- You didn't know?
- Did you see her leave yourself?

187
00:09:32,010 --> 00:09:33,440
The last time I saw her was last night.

188
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:36,880
- When I woke up, she'd gone to New York.
- Did you notice anything strange?

189
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:38,980
Not that I know of.

190
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,720
The CEO isn't the type to go abroad
without telling me.

191
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,760
And what's more, her phone is off.

192
00:09:45,860 --> 00:09:47,760
And I haven't been able to reach
Manager Lee all day.

193
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:52,700
She should have landed in New York by now.
Something is definitely wrong.

194
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,320
Lee Kang Hyuk.

195
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:20,890
You already heard Chae Hwa Young
pin everything on you.

196
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,890
If you don't tell the truth right now,

197
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:25,160
you'll spend the rest
of your life in here.

198
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:28,200
Tell me...

199
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,670
how you killed my Seo Rin!

200
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,600
Hey!

201
00:10:41,210 --> 00:10:42,450
Propofol...

202
00:10:42,450 --> 00:10:43,510
Propofol?

203
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,480
To Seo Rin,
as she lay on the operating table,

204
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:49,550
are you saying Chae Hwa Young herself
injected a lethal dose of Propofol?

205
00:10:49,990 --> 00:10:50,990
The injection...

206
00:10:52,990 --> 00:10:56,060
- The doctor did it.
- Why, you...

207
00:10:56,690 --> 00:10:59,660
You son of a witch. Hey, you bastards.

208
00:11:00,230 --> 00:11:03,400
You killed my precious granddaughter.

209
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:05,270
My Seo Rin.

210
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:09,410
And you let her die
on that cold operating table?

211
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:17,620
Chairman... Secretary Kim.

212
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:29,130
What happened?

213
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:30,800
Did Lee Kang Hyuk talk?

214
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:34,930
Yes. The cause of Seo Rin's death...

215
00:11:35,530 --> 00:11:37,900
was an overdose of a sleeping drug.

216
00:11:39,970 --> 00:11:40,970
What?

217
00:11:41,570 --> 00:11:42,840
You mean...

218
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:46,010
Chae Hwa Young did it with her own hands?

219
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:48,910
According to Lee Kang Hyuk,
a bribed doctor did it.

220
00:11:49,610 --> 00:11:52,820
After hearing the doctored recording
of Chae Hwa Young's voice,

221
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:56,150
he had a change of heart
and barely managed to tell us that much.

222
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,760
On that cold operating table...

223
00:11:59,990 --> 00:12:03,360
How scared she must have been.

224
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,600
My dear Seo Rin.

225
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:05,760
Mom.

226
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:27,380
Are you awake?

227
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:30,650
Lawyer Kang.

228
00:12:37,730 --> 00:12:38,730
Here, drink this.

229
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,610
I don't know if you heard,

230
00:12:54,950 --> 00:12:56,850
but Manager Lee just told everything.

231
00:12:57,450 --> 00:13:00,320
He confessed that
you ordered him to do all of it.

232
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,090
So stop being difficult...

233
00:13:02,450 --> 00:13:03,950
and just tell the truth.

234
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:07,190
You think I'd believe that?

235
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,090
Not a chance.

236
00:13:15,770 --> 00:13:16,870
(Voice Recording)

237
00:13:16,930 --> 00:13:18,270
Propofol...

238
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:20,670
To Seo Rin,
as she lay on the operating table,

239
00:13:20,740 --> 00:13:23,510
are you saying Chae Hwa Young herself
injected a lethal dose of Propofol?

240
00:13:23,510 --> 00:13:24,580
The injection...

241
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:27,950
The doctor did it.

242
00:13:28,210 --> 00:13:29,280
Did you hear that?

243
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:32,680
Lee Kang Hyuk betrayed you.

244
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:36,890
He said you ordered him to do everything.
He told us everything.

245
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,460
So tell the truth.

246
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:55,310
What's so funny?

247
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,410
Kang Baek Ho.

248
00:13:57,940 --> 00:13:59,110
No, Choi Ha Joon.

249
00:14:01,210 --> 00:14:02,310
Right now...

250
00:14:02,950 --> 00:14:05,550
this is no time for you
to be Chairman Ma's stooge.

251
00:14:06,450 --> 00:14:08,550
You should be working with me,

252
00:14:09,050 --> 00:14:11,490
so what on earth are you doing
barking up the wrong tree?

253
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:15,390
- What nonsense are you talking about?
- Has Jun Ho...

254
00:14:16,090 --> 00:14:17,090
not told you anything yet?

255
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:19,800
What lies did you tell to manipulate
General Manager Kang Jun Ho this time?

256
00:14:20,430 --> 00:14:22,530
Is the thought of going down alone
that unbearable?

257
00:14:22,830 --> 00:14:24,940
Is that why you're dragging
my brother down with you?

258
00:14:24,940 --> 00:14:26,670
And pulling him into hell with you
will make you feel better?

259
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,470
I didn't manipulate anyone.

260
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:30,640
I simply...

261
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:34,550
told the truth to poor Choi Ha Joon...

262
00:14:35,310 --> 00:14:37,180
who was being used not knowing anything.

263
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:40,220
- The truth?
- What Chairman Ma did...

264
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:44,390
to your grandfather in the past...

265
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,690
Never trust Chairman Ma.

266
00:14:49,090 --> 00:14:52,430
Not Chairman Ma, nor his family,
Oh Jang Mi and Jung Suk Hee.

267
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:55,470
They are all your sworn enemies.

268
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:58,570
Sworn enemies? That's absurd.

269
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:00,770
Go to Chairman Ma's study
and find the evidence.

270
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:07,780
Baek Ho. Did Chae Hwa Young talk?

271
00:15:09,210 --> 00:15:12,450
Well, it doesn't matter.
We don't need her testimony anymore.

272
00:15:12,950 --> 00:15:16,420
Baek Ho, my mom made dinner for you.
She knows how hard you've been working.

273
00:15:16,490 --> 00:15:18,190
Let's go up so you can eat while it's hot.

274
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:19,620
Okay.

275
00:15:24,230 --> 00:15:27,200
Chae Hwa Young,
I see you still have the strength...

276
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:29,600
to spin lies
with that cunning tongue of yours.

277
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:31,440
You're really something else.

278
00:15:37,470 --> 00:15:40,540
Did Kang Hyuk really confess everything?

279
00:15:41,250 --> 00:15:43,480
No way. That's impossible.

280
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:48,290
Here.

281
00:15:49,620 --> 00:15:50,950
Try some with salt.

282
00:15:51,860 --> 00:15:55,090
I wonder if young people
even like chicken soup these days.

283
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,770
I love anything you make for me.

284
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,470
Let me try some.

285
00:16:05,370 --> 00:16:06,440
This is delicious.

286
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:08,010
You should have some too.

287
00:16:08,070 --> 00:16:09,070
Here.

288
00:16:11,710 --> 00:16:14,110
It tastes even better
coming from my son-in-law.

289
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:17,850
- You landed a great son-in-law, Mom?
- I did. He's wonderful.

290
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:21,020
- It's delicious, isn't it?
- Of course. My mom made it.

291
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:26,090
- Give me some too.
- Okay.

292
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:27,660
Here you go.

293
00:16:28,230 --> 00:16:29,790
What in the world is going on?

294
00:16:30,730 --> 00:16:33,730
How can it be that
Suk Hee is perfectly fine?

295
00:16:36,570 --> 00:16:37,570
Excuse me.

296
00:16:38,370 --> 00:16:40,840
I made some chicken soup. Please join us.

297
00:16:42,040 --> 00:16:44,010
I'm not really in the mood
for chicken soup today.

298
00:16:47,110 --> 00:16:48,810
But, Suk Hee,

299
00:16:49,610 --> 00:16:53,680
you have a completely different air
about you today.

300
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:56,220
It's like you've totally changed.

301
00:16:57,760 --> 00:16:59,590
- Do I?
- Oh my.

302
00:17:00,290 --> 00:17:02,890
And you're speaking normally,
not like a fool.

303
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,230
Then...

304
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:07,730
does that mean you're sane again?

305
00:17:08,100 --> 00:17:10,500
Unfortunately for you, I am.

306
00:17:10,770 --> 00:17:11,770
What?

307
00:17:12,040 --> 00:17:16,310
Then you remember everything
that happened?

308
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:18,180
That you lured me out...

309
00:17:18,710 --> 00:17:20,480
and handed me over to Lee Kang Hyuk.

310
00:17:21,150 --> 00:17:25,250
And that Chae Hwa Young
almost killed me because of it.

311
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:28,050
I remember all of it vividly.

312
00:17:35,430 --> 00:17:38,830
Hong Ju, we have a huge problem.
It's about Jung Suk Hee.

313
00:17:39,030 --> 00:17:42,170
Oh Jang Mi's mother, Jung Suk Hee.
That fool...

314
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,330
She's gotten her memory back.

315
00:17:44,570 --> 00:17:47,840
What? Jung Suk Hee got her memory back?

316
00:17:47,940 --> 00:17:49,210
I'm telling you, she did.

317
00:17:49,410 --> 00:17:53,880
I think
when she grabbed Hwa Young by the hair...

318
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,080
and tore into her at Seo Rin's funeral,

319
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:58,520
I think her memory was already back then.

320
00:17:58,620 --> 00:18:00,750
Mom, that's not the problem right now.

321
00:18:00,980 --> 00:18:03,590
CEO Chae and Manager Lee Kang Hyuk
have gone missing.

322
00:18:03,650 --> 00:18:06,520
What? I thought Hwa Young left
for New York at dawn.

323
00:18:06,590 --> 00:18:10,060
General Manager Kang here had a detective
he knows check her departure records,

324
00:18:10,130 --> 00:18:12,000
and the detective said
CEO Chae never left the country.

325
00:18:12,330 --> 00:18:13,500
There's no record of it.

326
00:18:14,870 --> 00:18:16,830
Do you think she ran off
on a romantic getaway...

327
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:18,270
with Professor Kang Nam Bong?

328
00:18:18,670 --> 00:18:21,100
I'm asking if she didn't just skip town
without the Chairman knowing.

329
00:18:30,610 --> 00:18:32,580
This is Kang Jun Ho. I called you earlier.

330
00:18:33,850 --> 00:18:36,290
Detective, could I ask you one more thing?

331
00:18:37,290 --> 00:18:39,490
Could you please check
where the last place...

332
00:18:39,490 --> 00:18:41,190
that pinged
CEO Chae Hwa Young's phone was?

333
00:18:41,290 --> 00:18:42,530
Manager Lee Kang Hyuk's as well.

334
00:18:44,330 --> 00:18:46,230
This is urgent,
so I need it done as soon as possible.

335
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:47,900
Thanks.

336
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:54,340
Yes, Father.

337
00:18:54,340 --> 00:18:57,440
Jun Ho, I still can't get ahold
of Hwa Young.

338
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:58,510
Did something happen?

339
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:00,010
CEO Chae...

340
00:19:01,180 --> 00:19:02,450
I think she's been kidnapped...

341
00:19:02,980 --> 00:19:05,080
- by Chairman Ma's people.
- What?

342
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:15,760
It's just frustrating
that you know nothing about the Chairman.

343
00:19:16,230 --> 00:19:17,730
Just because
he's Oh Jang Mi's grandfather,

344
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:19,860
does that automatically
make him a good person?

345
00:19:19,930 --> 00:19:22,970
Not Chairman Ma, nor his family,
Oh Jang Mi and Jung Suk Hee.

346
00:19:23,470 --> 00:19:25,200
They are all your sworn enemies.

347
00:19:29,970 --> 00:19:31,340
Kang Baek Ho.

348
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:32,340
Baek Ho.

349
00:19:33,010 --> 00:19:34,010
Yes, Dad.

350
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,110
You brat.

351
00:19:37,650 --> 00:19:40,320
- What's wrong?
- You punk. Is this how I raised you?

352
00:19:40,980 --> 00:19:42,790
How could you kidnap someone?

353
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:46,690
Where is Hwa Young?
Where did you take that delicate woman?

354
00:19:50,730 --> 00:19:52,630
Kang Nam Bong, have you lost your mind?

355
00:19:52,900 --> 00:19:54,830
Who do you think you are,
hitting my precious son?

356
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:57,000
Stay out of this
if you don't know anything.

357
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:59,270
This brat, Kang Baek Ho,
kidnapped someone.

358
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:01,540
Who would Baek Ho kidnap?

359
00:20:01,540 --> 00:20:03,040
Get your facts straight
before you say another word.

360
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:04,980
Dad, you don't know anything,

361
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:06,910
but you're taking CEO Chae's side
no matter what, aren't you?

362
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:09,510
No matter what she did,
kidnapping is not the answer.

363
00:20:09,580 --> 00:20:11,150
What are you talking about?

364
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,920
Baek Ho, what's this about a kidnapping?

365
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:16,320
Do you have any idea
what Chae Hwa Young did?

366
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:18,690
To hide all her crimes,

367
00:20:18,990 --> 00:20:20,890
she even pretended to be
the Chairman's real daughter.

368
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:22,630
She knew Jang Mi's mother
was the real daughter...

369
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:24,460
- and did it to stop her.
- Shut up.

370
00:20:24,460 --> 00:20:27,600
She also killed Seo Rin.
Despite being a murderer and a thief,

371
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:30,430
- you're on her side, aren't you, Dad?
- Why you...

372
00:20:31,840 --> 00:20:32,940
Put your hand down.

373
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:36,310
Look at you.
Now you're resorting to violence?

374
00:20:36,570 --> 00:20:39,580
Go on, go find
that poor, delicate Chae Hwa Young.

375
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:41,880
- Just get out.
- Darn it.

376
00:20:42,780 --> 00:20:44,680
Hwa Young did nothing wrong.
It's Chairman Ma...

377
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:46,220
who's slandering her, you hear me?

378
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:49,190
And Baek Ho, get your head on straight.

379
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:55,690
I can't believe that man.

380
00:20:57,560 --> 00:20:58,560
Baek Ho.

381
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:01,130
But is it really true?

382
00:21:02,130 --> 00:21:03,930
You want me to move into this house?

383
00:21:04,270 --> 00:21:08,540
Yes. It's time to let everyone know
you're my daughter.

384
00:21:08,810 --> 00:21:10,440
I know how you feel, Father.

385
00:21:10,970 --> 00:21:14,750
But realistically,
the fallout would be huge.

386
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:19,750
For starters, Dong Seok and I
are siblings on paper.

387
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:25,020
And at the company,
there will be a period of intense turmoil.

388
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:27,790
Eun Hye, I...

389
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:30,230
For me, just being able to see you
like this...

390
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:32,430
is enough to make me happy.

391
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:37,730
Besides, you first have to make up
for the 50 years...

392
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:39,600
we couldn't spend together.

393
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:42,740
And more than Dream,

394
00:21:43,410 --> 00:21:45,010
making these memories with you...

395
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:48,110
is what's most important
and precious to me.

396
00:21:49,950 --> 00:21:51,450
Even so,

397
00:21:53,620 --> 00:21:55,450
your father...

398
00:21:57,050 --> 00:21:59,860
doesn't have much time left.

399
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,090
In the time I have left,

400
00:22:02,630 --> 00:22:06,260
I want to give you everything
I possibly can.

401
00:22:06,900 --> 00:22:09,670
But I already have everything
I could ever want.

402
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:16,040
Oh, dear.

403
00:22:16,770 --> 00:22:18,280
I'm fine.

404
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:21,480
Baek Ho.

405
00:22:22,650 --> 00:22:23,880
I think...

406
00:22:24,610 --> 00:22:25,850
I have to get a divorce.

407
00:22:27,280 --> 00:22:29,620
Honestly, I'm furious,

408
00:22:30,120 --> 00:22:31,660
but I can't shake
these lingering feelings.

409
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:35,090
I've been holding on,
hoping things might change,

410
00:22:36,630 --> 00:22:39,600
but seeing him so blinded by that woman
that he'd even strike his own son...

411
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:44,100
made me realize how pointless
both my love and my anger really are.

412
00:22:44,470 --> 00:22:45,470
Mom.

413
00:22:46,870 --> 00:22:49,970
No matter what, I'm on your side.
You know that, right?

414
00:22:51,210 --> 00:22:53,710
Of course I do, my son.

415
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:58,120
And don't do it for my sake.

416
00:22:59,050 --> 00:23:00,780
Mom, make this decision for yourself.

417
00:23:01,080 --> 00:23:03,250
I've wanted to divorce him for a while.

418
00:23:04,190 --> 00:23:08,290
But he has to pay the price
for betraying me.

419
00:23:09,730 --> 00:23:11,500
Maybe it's because I have a mean streak.

420
00:23:12,230 --> 00:23:14,560
I just can't stand losing.

421
00:23:14,770 --> 00:23:18,700
If someone hits me,
I have to hit them back to feel satisfied.

422
00:23:19,800 --> 00:23:23,870
- I'm pretty mean, aren't I?
- No, I love that about you, Mom.

423
00:23:24,370 --> 00:23:27,980
- It keeps the world fair. Tit for tat.
- Tat.

424
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:34,280
What?

425
00:23:34,580 --> 00:23:38,860
You're saying CEO Chae's phone
was last tracked to Chairman Ma's house?

426
00:23:40,260 --> 00:23:41,490
Okay, I understand.

427
00:23:48,900 --> 00:23:50,070
In that case,

428
00:23:50,630 --> 00:23:55,370
she might be held captive
somewhere in Chairman Ma's house.

429
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:02,980
If you need some muscle, call this number.

430
00:24:03,410 --> 00:24:04,580
They're my guys.

431
00:24:15,490 --> 00:24:18,530
Hello, this is Kang Jun Ho,
CEO Chae Hwa Young's son.

432
00:24:19,900 --> 00:24:21,030
And Manager Lee Kang Hyuk...

433
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:23,600
Yes, that's right.

434
00:24:25,900 --> 00:24:29,610
But Manager Lee Kang Hyuk is missing now.

435
00:24:29,910 --> 00:24:32,440
So, I was hoping you could find him.

436
00:24:33,410 --> 00:24:37,180
Tomorrow, tail my younger brother
Kang Baek Ho's car.

437
00:24:37,250 --> 00:24:39,050
You should be able to find
Manager Lee's location that way.

438
00:24:40,650 --> 00:24:42,350
This is urgent, so please do it quickly.

439
00:24:50,290 --> 00:24:52,900
Things won't go your way, Kang Jun Ho.

440
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,270
Good morning.

441
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:01,840
Team Leader Jin, look.

442
00:25:01,840 --> 00:25:03,770
There's an announcement
on the company bulletin board.

443
00:25:08,250 --> 00:25:11,180
Director Ma became General Manager.

444
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:16,650
(Personnel Announcement: Dismissal and
New Appointment of Management)

445
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:19,990
(Ma Seo Rin, Promoted,
Kang Jun Ho, Removed from Duty)

446
00:25:20,490 --> 00:25:23,760
Grandfather switched my position
with General Manager Kang's.

447
00:25:24,900 --> 00:25:26,560
(Ma Seo Rin, Promoted,
Kang Jun Ho, Removed from Duty)

448
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:27,560
What is this?

449
00:25:28,430 --> 00:25:30,170
Did Chairman Ma just demote me?

450
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:35,410
Jun Ho, what's going on?

451
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,770
That's what I'd like to know.

452
00:25:38,170 --> 00:25:40,110
How can the Chairman
make a personnel decision like this...

453
00:25:40,110 --> 00:25:41,240
all by himself?

454
00:25:42,180 --> 00:25:44,380
As if kidnapping and locking up CEO Chae
wasn't enough.

455
00:25:58,560 --> 00:26:01,630
They're really determined
to let me die in here.

456
00:26:04,100 --> 00:26:05,170
No way.

457
00:26:06,370 --> 00:26:08,710
I can't just die in here for nothing.

458
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:10,740
I must get it together.

459
00:26:11,710 --> 00:26:13,340
I can't just give up.

460
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:18,580
(Director Kang Jun Ho)

461
00:26:36,730 --> 00:26:39,100
(Director Kang Jun Ho)

462
00:26:39,170 --> 00:26:40,500
Yes, this is he.

463
00:26:41,710 --> 00:26:44,640
- What's the update?
- We've located Manager Lee.

464
00:26:45,080 --> 00:26:46,480
We'll go rescue him right away.

465
00:26:47,080 --> 00:26:48,080
Okay.

466
00:26:48,650 --> 00:26:49,650
I'm counting on you.

467
00:27:23,010 --> 00:27:24,680
I'll hit you. Stay back.

468
00:27:31,390 --> 00:27:32,420
Boss.

469
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:35,960
- Let's go.
- Darn...

470
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:44,600
(Staffing Services, Housekeeper)

471
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:55,380
- Manager Lee.
- Jun Ho.

472
00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:58,480
You've been through a lot.

473
00:27:59,020 --> 00:28:00,080
I'm okay.

474
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:02,950
Anyway, what about CEO Chae?
What happened to her?

475
00:28:03,820 --> 00:28:05,360
I've made a plan to get her out today.

476
00:28:06,260 --> 00:28:07,320
Where is she?

477
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:09,160
At Chairman Ma's house.

478
00:28:10,090 --> 00:28:11,090
Chairman Ma's house?

479
00:28:16,900 --> 00:28:18,200
Help me.

480
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:22,240
Help me.

481
00:28:24,810 --> 00:28:26,340
Help me.

482
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:50,470
(The First Man)

483
00:28:50,570 --> 00:28:53,970
- Is someone there?
- Is that Jun Ho? My son, Jun Ho?

484
00:28:54,140 --> 00:28:56,170
- Mom.
- Jun Ho, my son.

485
00:28:57,440 --> 00:29:00,410
Is this the nurse
who was wearing the smartwatch...

486
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:02,210
in Seo Rin's operating room?

487
00:29:02,510 --> 00:29:05,780
She must be hiding somewhere right now,
looking for a job.

488
00:29:06,120 --> 00:29:09,150
In the end,
Chairman Ma is forcing my hand.

489
00:29:09,320 --> 00:29:11,350
He's really sealed his fate.

490
00:29:11,620 --> 00:29:14,690
Jung Suk Hee and Oh Jang Mi,
you're all finished now, too.

491
00:29:15,860 --> 00:29:17,860
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
